data.description: 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath townhouse. Great floorplan with a large family room. Kitchen has been updated with newer appliances and white cabinets.  Lots and lots of storage.  Private covered patio and privacy fenced backyard. A little TLC will go a long way in this house.  House sold as is.
